<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>360° Brand Diagnostic™ | WRITE MY SOCIALS</title>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600&family=Poppins:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

    <style>
        :root {
            --ink: #1a1a1a;
            --cream: #fdfdfd;
            --muted: #6a6a6a;
            --line: rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            background: var(--cream);
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ===== NAVIGATION ===== */
        .top-bar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            padding: 35px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1000;
            background: rgba(253, 253, 253, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--ink);
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .menu-btn {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.25em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .menu-icon { width: 20px; height: 1px; background: var(--ink); position: relative; }
        .menu-icon::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -6px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 1px; background: var(--ink); }

        /* SIDEBAR */
        .sidebar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; right: 0;
            width: 300px; height: 100%;
            background: #fff;
            z-index: 2000;
            padding: 100px 40px;
            transform: translateX(100%);
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
            box-shadow: -10px 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
        }

        .menu-open .sidebar { transform: translateX(0); }

        .sidebar-links { list-style: none; }
        .sidebar-links li { margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .sidebar-links a { 
            text-decoration: none; color: var(--muted); 
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; 
        }

        /* ===== HERO ===== */
        .page-header {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 220px 24px 100px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5em;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            display: block;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            font-weight: 400;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* ===== CONTENT ===== */
        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 140px; }

        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
            gap: 120px;
            align-items: start;
            margin-bottom: 120px;
        }

        .deliverables-card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 60px;
        }

        .deliverables-list { list-style: none; }
        .deliverables-list li { margin-bottom: 35px; }
        .deliverables-list strong {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* ===== QUESTIONNAIRE ===== */
        .form-section {
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 0 auto 120px;
            padding: 80px 60px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
        }

        .form-intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--ink);
        }

        .form-group input, 
        .form-group textarea, 
        .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            background: transparent;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.4s ease;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .form-group input:focus, 
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            border-bottom-color: var(--ink);
            color: var(--ink);
        }

        .form-group textarea {
            height: 80px;
            resize: none;
        }

        /* ===== BUTTONS ===== */
        .pricing-box {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        }

        .cta-button {
            text-decoration: none;
            background: var(--ink);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 22px 45px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.3em;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid var(--ink);
        }

        .cta-button.secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--ink); margin-left: 20px; }

        .cta-button:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 60px; }
            .form-section { padding: 40px 24px; }
            .cta-button.secondary { margin-left: 0; margin-top: 20px; width: 100%; }
            .cta-button { width: 100%; text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body id="body">

<header class="top-bar">
    <a href="/" class="logo">WRITE MY SOCIALS</a>
    <button class="menu-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('body').classList.toggle('menu-open')">
        <span>Menu</span>
        <div class="menu-icon"></div>
    </button>
</header>

<nav class="sidebar">
    <ul class="sidebar-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services.html">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about.html">About</a></li>
    </ul>
</nav>

<header class="page-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">Strategic Audit • Private Strategy</span>
    <h1>360° Brand Diagnostic™</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--muted); max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; font-weight: 300;">An immersive, high-fidelity audit of your digital ecosystem, market positioning, and conversion architecture.</p>
</header>

<main class="container">
    <div class="grid-2">
        <div>
            <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:400; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:30px;">Clarity over Guesswork.</h2>
            <p style="color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:20px;">This audit identifies exactly where your brand is leaking authority, trust, and sales. It provides the "why" behind your current performance and a defined roadmap for what to fix first.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="deliverables-card">
            <ul class="deliverables-list">
                <li>
                    <strong>The Perception Audit</strong>
                    <span style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--muted);">A clinical teardown of your current positioning vs. market leaders.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>The 90-Day Roadmap</strong>
                    <span style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--muted);">A prioritized action plan for immediate content pillars and growth.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="form-section">
        <div class="form-intro">
            <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">The Intake</span>
            <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display'; font-weight:400; text-transform:uppercase;">Defining the Scope</h2>
            <p style="color:var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 15px;">Please review the information required to execute your diagnostic.</p>
        </div>

        <form>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Digital Footprint</label>
                <textarea placeholder="List your Website URL and primary Social Media handles (Instagram, LinkedIn, etc.)"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Primary Business Objective</label>
                <select>
                    <option value="" disabled selected>Select your current focus</option>
                    <option>Establish Authority & Thought Leadership</option>
                    <option>Lead Generation for High-Ticket Services</option>
                    <option>Product Sales / E-commerce Scaling</option>
                    <option>Community Growth & Engagement</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>The Target Audience</label>
                <textarea placeholder="Who are you speaking to? Describe your ideal client's biggest pain point."></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Market Comparison</label>
                <textarea placeholder="Identify 2-3 brands or competitors you admire or want to outperform."></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Revenue Gap</label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="What is your current monthly revenue vs. your 12-month goal?">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>The Top Objection</label>
                <textarea placeholder="What is the #1 reason people hesitate to buy from you?"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Current Frustration</label>
                <textarea placeholder="What part of your digital presence feels the most 'off' to you right now?"></textarea>
            </div>
        </form>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-box">
        <p style="font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 40px; color: var(--muted);">Ready to begin the diagnostic?</p>
        <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/14AeVd3hq4S55T83QD24003" class="cta-button">Standard Delivery</a>
        <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/cNi3cvcS02JX1CS0Er24002" class="cta-button secondary">Priority 48hr Rush</a>
    </section>
</main>

</body>
</html>
